OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: James
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,FJames Belcher, Age 98, Royal Marines
OL,8,FInterviewed 21 February 2024
OL,10,FA Royal Marine who was one of the
OL,11,Ffirst to arrive at Gold Beach at about
OL,12,F5.30am ahead of the Navy's aerial
OL,13,Fbombardment and troop landings, Mr
OL,14,FBelcher was part of a three-man crew
OL,15,Fon a landing craft.
OL,17,FThe crew had previously been training
OL,18,Fon assault craft, practising how to
OL,19,Fget troops onto shore, before
OL,20,Ftravelling to Portsmouth.
