OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: James
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,FTheir first job was to drop off about
OL,7,F14 soldiers from the Special Boat
OL,8,FSquadron.
OL,10,F"When we were going to the beach I
OL,11,Flooked up into the sky and it was full
OL,12,Fof aircraft but when we landed it was
OL,13,Fquiet," Mr Belcher said.
OL,15,F"As soon as we came away the
OL,16,Fbattleships started to fire off.
OL,18,F"We were landing these soldiers onto
OL,19,Fthe beach. I think there were only 14
OL,20,Fon the boat."
