OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: James
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,FThose soldiers were tasked with
OL,7,Fclearing X-shaped obstacles known as
OL,8,FCzech hedgehogs from the beach.
OL,10,F"They were designed to catch and
OL,11,Fdamage landing craft and the Allies
OL,12,Fwanted them removed or dismantled
OL,13,Fbefore troops landed.
OL,15,FHe said: "Each one of those had
OL,16,Fexplosives on and they had to take
OL,17,Fthem off.
OL,19,F"We were landing these soldiers onto
OL,20,Fthe beach."
