OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: James
OL,4,CBelcher
OL,6,FThe landing craft returned to
OL,7,FPortsmouth and returned later to the
OL,8,FAmerican sector, where many troops had
OL,9,Ffaced heavy fire on D-Day.
OL,11,F"Terrible, terrible," he said.
OL,13,F"There were bodies in the sea.
OL,15,F"Worst thing I have ever seen. Some of
OL,16,Fthe American landing craft had sunk
OL,17,Fbeforehand.
OL,19,F"And when we were coming away we hit a
OL,20,Fmine - panic, panic.
